replies.bodyText:
@gpang it is actually unnecessary to use String.format in log4j,
as long as you pass a Throwable as the last arg and the full log of exception will be printed .
We've been leveraging this undocumented feature for a long time in this codebase. Also check it out at https://stackoverflow.com/a/51781806/3161750
